│ 286 /// Returns the number of elements of the given type \p Ty, not greater │
│ than \p                                                                     │
│ 287 /// Sz, which forms type, which splits by \p TTI into whole vector      │
│ types during                                                                │
│ 288 /// legalization.                                                       │
│ 289 static unsigned                                                         │
│ 290 getFloorFullVectorNumberOfElements(const TargetTransformInfo &TTI, Type │
│ *Ty,                                                                        │
